00087 void MSD_lowDisplayHidden(CTYPE *cptr)
00088 {
00089    SPTYPE optr;
00090    DPTYPE dptr;
00091    FPTYPE rf;
00092    FPTYPE lf;
00093    EPTYPE eptr;
00094    vector sv, ev, edir;
00095 
00096    g_frame();
00097    MSD_lowDetermineVisibility(cptr);
00098    divedge = (DEDGTYPE *)workbuf;
00099    for (AllSolids(optr))
00100    {
00101       if (SolDsp(optr) != TRUE)
00102       {
00103          continue;
00104       }
00105       g_pcolor(MSD_lowGetSolidColor(optr));
00106       for (AllShellsSolid(optr, dptr))
00107       {
00108          for (AllEdgesShell(dptr, eptr))
00109          {
00110             if (breakflg)
00111             {
00112                return;
00113             }
00114             switch (EdgEVis(eptr))
00115             {
00116                 case INVISIBLE:
00117                 if ((cptr->dash == TRUE) && (EdgEClp(eptr) == TRUE))
00118                 {
00119                    veccopy(sv, EdgSVClp2(eptr));
00120                    veccopy(ev, EdgEVClp2(eptr));
00121                    g_tline(DASHED_LINE, sv, ev);
00122                 }
00123                 break;
00124 
00125                 case _VISIBLE:
00126                 if (EdgEClp(eptr) == TRUE)
00127                 {
00128                    veccopy(desvtx, EdgSVClp3(eptr));
00129                    veccopy(deevtx, EdgEVClp3(eptr));
00130                    MSD_lowUpdateDEBox();
00131                    divednum = 0;
00132                    divedptr = divedge;
00133                    MSD_lowAddEdgeDivision(desvtx);
00134                    rf = LooLFace(HalWLoop(EdgHe1(eptr)));
00135                    lf = LooLFace(HalWLoop(EdgHe2(eptr)));
00136                    MSD_lowEdgeEdgeIntersection(optr, eptr, lf, rf);
00137                    MSD_lowEdgeFaceIntersection(optr, SNIL, lf, rf);
00138                    MSD_lowAddEdgeDivision(deevtx);
00139                    MSD_lowSortDividedEdge();
00140                    veccopy(sv, VerVCoord(HalVtx(EdgHe1(eptr))));
00141                    veccopy(ev, VerVCoord(HalVtx(EdgHe2(eptr))));
00142                    vecminus(edir, ev, sv);
00143                    if (normalize(edir) == TRUE)
00144                    {
00145                       MSD_lowSetEdgeVisibility('e', lf, rf, edir);
00146                       MSD_lowDisplayDividedEdge(cptr, eptr);
00147                    }
00148                 }
00149                 break;
00150             }
00151          }
00152       }
00153    }
00154 }
